fields.value: Raw behavioral data for "Robust neurocognitive individual differences in grammatical agreement processing: A latent variable approach"

dsDescriptionValue.value: These are the raw output files from the behavioral acceptability judgment task run concurrently with the EEG sentence processing experiment. For participants in the SPR task, word-by-word reading times are also included.  Files were generated by Paradigm Experimental software (http://www.paradigmexperiments.com/). See the readme in the general files dataset for more information on the information in the files. The R code for compiling, processing and analyzing data is included in the "Analysis scripts and outputs" dataset associated with this dataverse. All code and plots necessary for re-creating our analyses are included in those scripts, with relevant R distribution and package versions current as of April 2018 (R version 3.4.4).
